1. *Predivna* si osoba. (You are a wonderful person.)
2. Žena koja stoji tamo ima *predivne* oči. (The woman standing there has beautiful eyes.)
3. Ovo je *predivan* pogled sa vrha planine. (This is a stunning view from the top of the mountain.)
4. Zvuci ovog orkestra su *predivni*. (The sounds of this orchestra are beautiful.)
5. Proveli smo *predivno* veče zajedno. (We spent a wonderful evening together.)
6. *Predivnu* tortu sam napravila za rođendan. (I made a beautiful cake for the birthday.)
7. Ona nosi *predivnu* haljinu na venčanju. (She is wearing a gorgeous dress at the wedding.)
8. Tvoje reči su mi ulepšale dan, bila si *predivna*. (Your words made my day, you were lovely.)
9. Izgledaš *predivno* u toj novoj frizuri. (You look fabulous with that new hairstyle.)
10. Cvetovi u bašti su *predivni* ove godine. (The flowers in the garden are beautiful this year.)